parameters.name: UT
parameters.description: Universal Time given in PDS format: yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sss.

parameters.name: BZ_SC
parameters.description:
BZ_SC: The Z-component of the magnetic field 
in the PVO Inertial Spacecraft Coordinate System (PVO_ISCC). The Z axis is    
defined to be anti-parallel to the spacecraft spin axis during orbital        
operations. This vector has been averaged over two spin periods from the      
high resolution data.

parameters.name: VAR_BZ
parameters.description:
VAR BZ: Variance of the BZ SC over the       
averaging window.

parameters.name: BN
parameters.description:
BT: An estimate of the magnetic field        
strength over the averaging interval.
